snippet.title: Undertale Red - Ending: Genocide
snippet.description:
A cool fangame made just a few hours ago! The entire gameplay is in the video (it's just a few minutes long). The author of this game is Taxiderby.

Here is the genocide ending.

You can download it here: http://taxiderby.tumblr.com/post/135354499621/hi-i-made-playable-undertale-tribute-made-from
